GD::XYScale
===========

Draws a 2D X-Y scale to use with scientific representations 
of the formulas, curves, geometric data etc...

Read the module's POD for documentation and examples.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

or under Windows:

   perl Makefile.PL
   nmake
   nmake test
   nmake install

See the resulting pictures from the tests for sample
graphics (if you "make test"). 

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules:

	GD

Which is available on CPAN.

